content:
It sounds like you're making great progress on planning your meals and making a shopping list. Remember to stay flexible and be open to adjusting your plan if you find any great deals or if your schedule changes.

Since you mentioned you went to Walmart last Saturday, I'm curious - did you happen to grab anything else besides the chicken breasts that you haven't used yet? Maybe some veggies or canned goods that you can incorporate into your meal plan?
